      "span_text": "The correctly constructed pMMB206-BdcA ( Figure 1 ) was introduced into the Rhizobium strain via electroporation and into the Pseudomonas strains via conjugation as previously described  . pMMB206-BdcA is a low-copy-number plasmid, and the expression of bdcA is under the control of the tandem tac-lacUV5 promoter  ."
